{"type": "article", "id": 43568, "title": "不说笑，这盏灯具，展示的真是“光在弦上”｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-07-30T23:13:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 42593, "name": "Dominique Ansel Bakery"}, {"id": 42805, "name": "Massess"}, {"id": 42806, "name": "ミドリ"}, {"id": 42807, "name": "Little Building Co"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 122, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170730203832SQwgzDuPbneit3Es.gif", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>Bo Light by Massess</h3><p>洛杉矶设计工作室 <a href=\"https://massess.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Massess</a> 的作品以极简风格为主，最近他们抱着探索材质与工艺极限的理念，打造了一款名为 Bo Light 的灯具。拱形的实橡木与黄铜线构成了一把弓的模样，只要轻轻触碰那条紧绷的弦，就可以操控橡木内侧 LED 灯的开关，非常讨巧。它既可以平放在桌面上，也可以作为壁灯使用。这是它的<a href=\"https://massess.com/collections/2017\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 250 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730203848wra1T2RMhm4tf6gk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730203848e5vxuzUf9E4b8jH7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730203849ArfomW76TkpxYLsN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730203849ef1HlaMmOCTQXd6J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730203848VfSGsCP1mZ6NDXqv.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"gif\">\n</figure></div><h3>Block Clip by ミドリ</h3><p>假如列一张“最容易弄丢的办公用品”排行榜，第一名很有可能是回形针这类体积比较小的夹子。针对这些小物的收纳问题，日本文具品牌 ミドリ（Midori）推出了将夹子和积木结合在一起的 <a href=\"http://www.midori-japan.co.jp/products/2017_03.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Block Clip</a>。它看起来就像是一款更扁平的乐高，分为两种尺寸。人们可以发挥想象力，将它们打造成笔筒、名片夹或是桌面装饰物。值得一提的是，Block Clip 还获得了今年日本文具大赏<a href=\"http://www.isot.jp/Award/\" rel=\"nofollow\">设计类的优胜奖</a>。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.midori-store.net/SHOP/5304/5355/list.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 540 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730203908Dj2a59qrVeMnctJb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652504\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730203908PEBX205VgGpHDK8o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730203908FRy0zLlv1sG7J8Zh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Farnsworth House by Little Building Co</h3><p>坚持“少即是多”（Less is more）的设计哲学，德国建筑师路德维希·密斯·凡德罗（Ludwig Mies van der Rohe）留下了不少以钢框架结构和玻璃为特色的建筑，其中最著名的或许就是第一个采用玻璃幕墙的范思沃斯住宅（Farnsworth house）。澳大利亚模型设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.littlebuildingco.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Little Building Co</a> 最近推出了这栋住宅的木制模型以及配套的盒子，满足设计爱好者的收藏欲。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/45445701/mies-van-de-rohes-farnsworth-house-architectural-m\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价从 120 澳元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707302041183GgDvfCzkBKrixjL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.701471\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730204118vHlLfEihZGOIw3sc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.650000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730204118Qqt2MWLTpHBasob9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730204118zeFSrmWCoAJalv7P.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Kiwi Sorbet Bar by Dominique Ansel Bakery</h3><p>我们曾在<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/43286.html\">夏日限定特辑</a>中介绍过混合甜点店 Dominique Ansel Bakery 推出的西瓜冰淇淋，而东京表参道分店近日又引进了以奇异果为灵感的冰淇淋三明治。这个“矩形奇异果”总共分为三层：中央是香草冰淇淋，它和绿色的奇异果雪芭之间撒有罂粟籽，最外层采用了普通的牛奶巧克力。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730203936u7eYcFEdip4onqMk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707302039369IGks4cHC2q1vYft.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730203936agQOvD23L17Eh0UT.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655000\" data-format=\"png\">\n</figure></div><h3>Won Der Cookie by Vsevolod Abramov &amp; David Hovhannisyan</h3><p>还记得<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/37486.html\">画中人眼罩</a>和<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/38747.html\">肤色防晒霜</a>吗？来自俄罗斯的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/sevaabr\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vsevolod Abramov</a> 和 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/DavidHovhannisyan\" rel=\"nofollow\">David Hovhannisyan</a> 也加入了这场由荷兰国立博物馆发起的衍生品设计比赛中，为这款名为 Won Der Cookie 的概念产品设计了包装。鉴于饼干中含有大麻成分，他们通过手机应用 FaceApp 让那些看起来有些严肃的画中人也能做出露齿的微笑，背面的原版和正面的笑容形成了有趣的对比。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730203950pSvyLGaEbtn3sYk0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.896667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730203950Ip6WmRZyMAxsHDLi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730203951uRLGfxbYyTiNHBke.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730203950o6v3pTRBxz8naZKG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.896667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Classic Camera series by Lee Ji-hee</h3><p>韩国艺术家 <a href=\"http://www.jihee-paperwork.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lee Ji-hee</a> 曾为不少品牌制作过以狗为主题的巨型纸雕。最近，她又推出了以复古相机为原型的 Classis Camera 系列。拥有平面设计背景的她这次并没有热衷于还原每个细节，而是使用了一组明快的配色，看起来就像是这些相机的当代版。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730204005u01MblrOwJ7kdEj9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.001127\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730204005PhaEs2W0DAqQNXgY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730204005wIGyDx8kq2noNOYc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170730204005bKVTpo2NgC8zXDYR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707302040066XJi4H3zOhWEc2y8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>"}